videos.headline: Felton reaches across goal line for UCLA TD
videos.description: Dorian Thompson-Robinson's pass finds Demetric Felton, who reaches across the goal line while being tackled to put UCLA up early.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Felton reaches across goal line for UCLA TD) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Taylor-Stuart's interception sets up USC's TD
videos.description: Isaac Taylor-Stuart intercepts Dorian Thompson-Robinson's pass to set up a Vavae Malepeai one-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Taylor-Stuart’s interception sets up USC’s TD) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Thompson-Robinson keeps it for UCLA TD
videos.description: Dorian Thompson-Robinson keeps it and runs into the end zone untouched.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Thompson-Robinson keeps it for UCLA TD) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pittman scores his 10th TD of the season
videos.description: Michael Pittman Jr. catches a one-yard touchdown pass from Kedon Slovis, his 10th touchdown reception of the season.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pittman scores his 10th TD of the season) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pittman grabs 2nd TD in first half
videos.description: Kedon Slovis finds Michael Pittman Jr. for a four-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pittman grabs 2nd TD in first half) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: London hauls in 32-yard TD pass
videos.description: Kedon Slovis heaves up a 32-yard touchdown pass to Drake London to put USC up 31-14.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (London hauls in 32-yard TD pass) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Slovis throws 49-yard TD pass in record-setting performance
videos.description: Kedon Slovis sends a 49-yard touchdown pass to Tyler Vaughns in the fourth quarter. Slovis later set the single-game passing record for USC with 515 yards.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Slovis throws 49-yard TD pass in record-setting performance) 2019/11/23 ESHEET
